{"id":"808629006080606208","type":"text","timestamp":1771168714,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/808629006080606208","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":true,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://sarinisanta.tumblr.com/post/808269956247650304/they-should-make-a-tarot-but-like-every-card-is\">sarinisanta</a>:</p><blockquote><p>They should make a tarot but like, every card is lesbians.</p><p>Like you could have the witch, the hanged woman, the empress twice, the she/her tower&hellip;</p><p>We could even use you as The World.</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"sarinisanta"},"post":{"id":"808269956247650304"}}],"baseline_notes":14,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}